once you have this, whate are you goign to do with it?

you need to set up an input variable createdate, then you have to pull it in to the workflow, then you need to take that date and apply the function to it and output the day of week
you have to put code in there for the code to work.

Set input fields
<https://share.zight.com/o0u1Poxq>

```exports.main = async (event, callback) =&gt; {
  const { createdate } = event.inputFields

  const date = new Date(Number(createdate))

  const day = date.getUTCDay()

  const output = day === 0 ? 7 : day;

  callback({
    outputFields: {
      dayOfWeek: output
    }
  });
}```
this prints 1 for monday, 2 for tuesday, etc.
